These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, apple
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, fantasy
1. the person watching zombie movies is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
2. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | cola      |
| Food          | apple | pomegranate    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks   | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, collecting
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, photographer
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, trike
1. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
3. the photographer is not to the right of the nurse##8
4. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | sprite        | juice    |
| Hobby       | writing         | collecting |
| Job         | photographer | nurse   |
| Transport   | quad-bike               | trike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, adventure
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, indie
There are 2 different nationalities: american, british
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish
1. the american is in an odd position##4
2. the british is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
3. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance       | adventure |
| Music-Genre   | house       | indie    |
| Nationality   | american | british |
| Pet           | rabbit        | fish   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
