The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, mechanic
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, australian
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, subway
1. the russian is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | fishing | puzzles  |
| Job           | mechanic  | police-officer |
| Nationality   | australian | russian   |
| Transport     | subway   | scooter |

